572
00:38:07,023 --> 00:38:08,068
Thanks, Jack.

573
00:38:09,025 --> 00:38:10,418
Excuse me.

574
00:38:10,418 --> 00:38:11,898
Mr. Shelby?

575
00:38:20,950 --> 00:38:22,778
Good. Very good.

576
00:38:23,997 --> 00:38:25,433
Jack Hayes.

577
00:38:25,433 --> 00:38:27,130
Katherine Barnes.
Nice to meet you.

578
00:38:28,393 --> 00:38:30,830
Well, I'll-I'll leave you
to Mr. Shelby.

579
00:38:30,830 --> 00:38:32,788
Once he starts talking
you can't shut him up.

580
00:38:35,313 --> 00:38:37,358
Nice to meet you, Mrs...

581
00:38:37,358 --> 00:38:38,446
Ms. Barnes.

582
00:38:38,446 --> 00:38:40,187
Ms... Whatever.

583
00:38:40,187 --> 00:38:41,928
