00:40:32,125 --> 00:40:33,605
He's starting to
sound like you.

617
00:40:35,215 --> 00:40:36,434
Goodbye.

618
00:40:55,453 --> 00:40:56,758
Kind of classy for you.

619
00:40:59,065 --> 00:41:00,458
You think so?

620
00:41:10,119 --> 00:41:11,643
What the hell's he doing?

621
00:41:11,643 --> 00:41:12,992
[COUGHING]

622
00:41:12,992 --> 00:41:14,689
