649
00:43:34,394 --> 00:43:35,961
Maybe she's at home.

650
00:43:37,223 --> 00:43:38,572
She'd want her toys.

651
00:43:39,138 --> 00:43:40,618
[SOBBING]

652
00:43:46,362 --> 00:43:47,712
