about cancer, Mr. Shelby,
not a common cold.

685
00:45:51,096 --> 00:45:52,358
Would you call me Frank?

686
00:45:55,578 --> 00:45:56,666
All right.

687
00:45:58,190 --> 00:46:00,627
Danny's got help.

688
00:46:00,627 --> 00:46:02,498
He's got more than most.
He's got you.

689
00:46:04,326 --> 00:46:07,199
And you gotta want it for him.
You can't give up.

690
00:46:07,199 --> 00:46:08,983
