you're talking about.

691
00:46:12,291 --> 00:46:13,683
You don't have any idea

692
00:46:13,683 --> 00:46:16,948
about the time,
and the care,
and the prayers.

693
00:46:18,906 --> 00:46:21,953
Don't you dare pass
judgment on me or Danny,

694
00:46:21,953 --> 00:46:24,433
because you are totally
ignorant of the people

695
00:46:24,433 --> 00:46:27,045
and the circumstances
involved, Frank.

696
00:46:34,748 --> 00:46:36,489
You're right.
I don't know you.

697
00:46:38,230 --> 00:46:40,536
But me and Danny,
we got something going.

698
00:46:42,756 --> 00:46:44,018
It's a man thing.

699
00:46:48,544 --> 00:46:50,416
