the only solution.

702
00:47:10,610 --> 00:47:12,786
Now, all I wanna do is
spend a little time
with your son.

703
00:47:12,786 --> 00:47:14,092
Just get to know him.

704
00:47:15,397 --> 00:47:17,225
No racing, no swearing.

705
00:47:19,837 --> 00:47:21,186
Just parts.

706
00:47:23,797 --> 00:47:25,277
That's...

707
00:47:25,277 --> 00:47:26,539
That's okay.

708
00:47:29,585 --> 00:47:30,717
Thanks.

709
00:47:34,895 --> 00:47:36,418
[STAMMERS]
I'm gonna go see Danny.

710
00:47:37,158 --> 00:47:38,377
It's my pleasure.

711
00:47:40,379 --> 00:47:41,554
Thanks for the time.

712
00:48:15,240 --> 00:48:16,589
You.

